Author: Spectrachic311311
Text: Once I saw this super thin lady at the thrift store and I was so jealous until she walked to the food pantry to get some stuff. I realized she was probably not that way by choice and I felt like such an asshole.

Author: alwaysrelapsing17
Text: love the guilt and jealousy that drowns me every time I dare to look up from my phone or friend group during a meal in the dining commons at my uni
